                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7685" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0236</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">3507 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">坚定前行：用友网络战略转型下的股权激励</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Moving forward firmly: Equity incentive under Yonyou&#39;s network strategy transformation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">任莉莉，金雨欣，姜伟雪，邹旭滨</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">燕山大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">用友网络科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">用友网络；股权激励；公司治理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Yonyou Network ；stock ownership incentive ; corporate governance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着现代企业制度的出现和发展，所有权与经营权出现两者分离的情况。股权激励机制的出现，让激励对象的身份由企业员工转变为企业股东，使得企业的战略目标、股东利益、管理者利益、员工利益达成一致。本案例以用友网络为例，基于企业战略视角探求股权激励与企业战略之间的关系，深入挖掘企业战略对股权激励设计方案的影响以及股权激励对企业战略的推进作用。本案例表明，企业的战略与股权激励在发展过程中并不是各自为安的，而是相互影响、相互促进的。希望通过该案例，引导学员掌握股权激励的相关理论，理解股权激励对企业实现发展战略的深远意义，同时也为我国上市公司从战略角度设计恰当的股权激励方案提供了一定的借鉴和参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the emergence and development of modern enterprise systems, there has been a separation of ownership and management rights. The equity incentive mechanisms has transformed the identity of incentive targets from employees to shareholders, achieving a consensus on the strategic goals, shareholder interests, management interests, and employee interests. Taking Yonyou as an example, this case explores the relationship between equity incentive and corporate strategy from the perspective of corporate strategy, and deeply explores the impact of corporate strategy on equity incentive design scheme and the role of equity incentive in promoting corporate strategy. This case demonstrates that the strategy and equity incentives are not mutually beneficial in the development process, but rather interact and promote each other. Tthrough this case study, students can be guided to master the relevant theories of equity incentives, understand the profound significance of equity incentives for enterprises to achieve development strategies, and also provide some reference for Chinese listed companies to design appropriate equity incentive plans from a strategic perspective.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">委托代理理论；激励理论；战略管理理论；契约理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-10</td>
                            </tr>
